{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ec5c6093c6","title":"对反映刘景范情况来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"73fdc95663","index":0,"year":1974,"month":12,"day":21,"articleId":"ec5c6093c6"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[{"id":"dd9a544e90","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ec5c6093c6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"根据毛泽东的批示，中共中央办公厅主任汪东兴1974年12月21日指出：“同桂荣同志写给毛主席的信，主席已有批示。此件请印发在京中央政治局同志。并送两份给中央专案组一办，遵照批示办理。"}],"contents":[{"id":"03484385e8","type":"title","text":"对反映刘景范情况来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ec5c6093c6"},{"id":"dd9a544e90","type":"paragraph","text":"此案审查已久，不必再拖了，建议宣布释放，免于追究","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ec5c6093c6"},{"id":"62fd5a168c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ec5c6093c6"},{"id":"17e14c561a","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月廿一日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ec5c6093c6"},{"id":"103122725d","type":"paragraph","text":"送汪主任药办","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ec5c6093c6"},{"id":"e8e0973a8c","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]地质部原副部长刘景范的嫂子同桂荣（刘志丹烈士的妻子）1974年12月17日给毛泽东等写信说，今天我去看望刘景范，发现他身体很坏，精神不好，惠有肝病、十二指肠溃肠病，手脚浮肿，肚子膨胀，可能是肝硬变，如果不及时治疗，担心坚持不了多长时间。特此请求：一、他的问题已经审查8年了，如果已经审查清楚，能否赶快把他释放出来治病？二、如果他的问题还不能下结论，是否可以把他放出来一面治病，一面继续审查？","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ec5c6093c6"}],"page":{"id":"9745003abc","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"ec5c6093c6","start":523,"end":523}}}},"__N_SSG":true}